ZOTAC-CART-PAYPALSTART 
  this script will refresh your cart every 10 seconds or so and when your item comes into stock will auto launch Paypal express and alert you.

ZOTAC-WISHLIST-ADDALLTOCART
  this script will refresh your wishlist every 10 seconds or so and when an item comes into stock will auto add all to cart.
  
  
Use a chrome extension like Tampermonkey to launch the scripts.
